<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Appointment Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .header,
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header img {
            width: 150px;
        }

        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .content {
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .details,
        .appointment-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .details {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .details p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .appointment-details ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .signature {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .footer-info {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .footer-info div {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .signature img {
            width: 100px;
        }

        .detail_container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="<%= company==='NTechzy Pvt. Limited' ?'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhlqc0ymy/image/upload/v1729940916/ems/jh2omdjjlqiywhqfufdy.png' : 'https://res.cloudinary.com/dhlqc0ymy/image/upload/v1731325192/ems/j1bd7cdfmtnklffqq8ld.png'  %>"
            alt="Logo">
    </div>

    <div class="title">
        APPOINTMENT LETTER
    </div>

    <div class="detail_container">
        <div class="details">
            <p> <b>Letter to:</b> <br /><br />
                <%= employeeName %>
            </p>

            <p>Human Resource<br /><br />
                <%= company %><br />
                    <%= companyAddress %>
            </p>
        </div>

        <% var currDate=new Date(); var day=("0" + currDate.getDate()).slice(-2); var month=("0" + (currDate.getMonth()
            + 1)).slice(-2); var year=currDate.getFullYear(); var formattedDate=day + "/" + month + "/" + year; var
            startDate=new Date(startDate); var startDateDay=("0" + startDate.getDate()).slice(-2); var
            startDateMonth=("0" + (startDate.getMonth() + 1)).slice(-2); var startDateYear=startDate.getFullYear(); var
            formattedstartDate=startDateDay + "/" + startDateMonth + "/" + startDateYear; %>
            <div>
                <p>
                    Date: <%= formattedDate %>
                </p>
            </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>To <%= employeeName %>,</strong></p>
        <p>Congratulations on successfully completing your probationary period! We are pleased to officially appoint you
            as a permanent member of our team in the position of <%= jobTitle %>, effective immediately.</p>

        <div class="appointment-details">
            <p>Appointment Details:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Position: <%= jobTitle %>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Department: <%= departmentName %>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Start Date: <%= formattedstartDate %>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="benefits">
            <p>Benefits:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provisional Fund</li>
                <li>Paid Time Off: <%= paidDaysOff %> days of paid leave annually, plus public holidays.</li>
                <li>Performance Bonuses: Opportunities for bonuses based on performance.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="additional-info">
            <p>Additional Information:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Tenure Bond: A tenure bond of <%= bondYears %> years is required, with a fee of <%= bondAmount %> if
                            you leave early.</li>
                <li>Notice Period: The notice period for resignation is <%= noticePeriod %> weeks/months.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p>We are excited to have you on board and look forward to your contributions. If you have any questions, please
            reach out.</p>

        <div class="signature">
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhlqc0ymy/image/upload/v1731483587/Screenshot_2024-11-13_130926_adno8m.png"
                    alt="Signature"></p>
            <p>
                Sneha Awasthi<br>Human Resources
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-info">
            <div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64C0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.1-46.3 11.6L304.7 368C234.3 334.7 177.3 277.7 144 207.3L193.3 167c13.7-11.2 18.4-30 11.6-46.3l-40-96z"/></svg>
                <span><%= company==='NTechzy Pvt. Limited' ?'+91 9125886480' : '+91 9125886480' %></span>
            </div>
            <div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M48 64C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112c0 15.1 7.1 29.3 19.2 38.4L236.8 313.6c11.4 8.5 27 8.5 38.4 0L492.8 150.4c12.1-9.1 19.2-23.3 19.2-38.4c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48L48 64zM0 176L0 384c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64l384 0c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64l0-208L294.4 339.2c-22.8 17.1-54 17.1-76.8 0L0 176z"/></svg>
                <span><%= company==='NTechzy Pvt. Limited' ?'hr@careerkick.in' : 'hr@careerkick.in' %></span>
         
            </div>
            <div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 384 512"><path d="M215.7 499.2C267 435 384 279.4 384 192C384 86 298 0 192 0S0 86 0 192c0 87.4 117 243 168.3 307.2c12.3 15.3 35.1 15.3 47.4 0zM192 128a64 64 0 1 1 0 128 64 64 0 1 1 0-128z"/></svg>
                <span>
                    <%= company==='NTechzy Pvt. Limited' ?'GF 37,SNG Plaza Near-Pari Chowk' : 'GF 37,SNG Plaza Near-Pari Chowk' %>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>